text: Tehachapi is a city in Kern County, California. It is in the mountains between the San Joaquin Valley and the Mojave Desert. Tehachapi had a population of 12,939 in 2020, comprising 8,225 males and 4,714 females. There are many more males than females because Tehachapi has a state prison. == References == Category:Cities in California Category:Settlements in Kern County, California
title: Tehachapi, California
